<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8308630>
    dc:description "FIGURE 36. Species of Rhadamanthus Salisb. 1. Rhadamanthus convallarioides (L.f.) Salisb. ex Baker from Jacquin (1797: t. 81, as Hyacinthus convallarioides L.f.); 2. Rhadamanthus urantherus R.A.Dyer from Dyer (1934: t. 3247); 3. Rhadamanthus cochlearis (Mart.- Azorín et al.) Mart.-Azorín et al. from Martínez-Azorín et al. (2013: 333, as Drimia cochlearis Mart.-Azorín et al.)." ;
